message: The beauty of #V4V is that you can chase the numbers and say, "I'm going to make a living off of this" or "I got bills to pay" all you want but at the end of the day it's all about the "feel" and "vibe" you get from it.   You can just cut all the BS and just have a great time doing stuff and see where it takes you.   It's the reason I'm typing this right now. I'm probably just crazy but I'm have a blast and this damn BoostBot has created a monster with these damn War and Peace Boostagram.
